mother and an American father

00:06:34.420 --> 00:06:39.280
and at the age of 9 in 1784,
just months after the revolution,

00:06:39.280 --> 00:06:41.850
she was made a citizen of Maryland,

00:06:41.850 --> 00:06:45.030
but that didn't mean
much to her then.

00:06:45.030 --> 00:06:48.510
